'''Godliver Gordian''' ni  filime yo muri  [[Tanzaniya]] . <ref name="TF">https://theafricanfilmfestival.org/Festival/Winners/2016</ref> Ni umwe mu bagize umuryango w’ubutabazi ushingiye i New York, Global Medical Relief Fund, kandi yafashije abarangije muri albino kubona akazi bavugana n’abakoresha mu izina ryabo, hatitawe ku bwoba bujyanye na albinos muri [[Tanzaniya]] . <ref>https://www.nationalgeographic.com/magazine/2017/06/albinism-health-genetics-society/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Gordian yari akanyenyeri muri Jordan Riber 2012 isaha  n'igice ya Swahili language TV Series , ''Siri ya Mtungi'', aho yagize uruhare "Cheusi". Muri iyi filime kandi hagaragayemo nka Beatrice Taisamo, Yvonne Cherrie n'abandi. <ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/siri-ya-mtungi/oclc/1019443274</ref> <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt2551356/?ref_=m_ttfc_tt</ref>

Muri 2015, yakinnye cyane muri firime yikinamico yo muri Tanzaniya ya Chande Omar yitwa, ''Aisha'' . <ref>https://www.evasguide.com/east-africa/movies/aisha-tanzania-movie/</ref> <ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.film.aisha.17220.html</ref>

Mu 2016, yari ku rutonde African Film na Arts Festival (Arta'atu) ibihembo mu ''Best Actress'' category, kubera uruhare yagize muri filimi, ''Aisha.''  Kuko uruhare kimwe no film, yari ku rutonde kuko Azam Bongo Movie Awards mu ''Best Actress'' category ku 2016 Zanzibar International Film Festival (ZIFF), <ref>https://africultures.com/evenements/?no=41938</ref> <ref>https://cineequal.org/3950-ziff-2016-award-winners/</ref> bikaba yatsindiye. <ref>https://www.filmcontact.com/news/tanzania/east-african-films-dominate-ziff-2016-awards</ref>

Yagaragaye kandi muri filime yo gusetsa-ikinamico ya 2016 na Seko Shamte yitwa, ''Gutaha'' . <ref>https://media.dream13.com/homecoming-2016/</ref> <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt5116212/</ref>

Yabaye umuyobozi wa casting muri 2017 yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi byamafirime yo mu bwoko bwa Tanzania y’igiswahili yakozwe na Amil Shivji yise, ''T-JUNCTION'', yakinnye: Magdalena Christopher, Hawa Alisa (Hawa Ally), Cojack Chilo. <ref>https://www.kijiweniproductions.com/films/tjunction</ref> <ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.film.t-junction.20117.html</ref>

Muri 2018, yakinnye muri filime y’ikinamico y’ururimi rw’igiswahili ya Jordan Riber, ''Bahasha (Ibahasha)'', aho yakinnye nka ''Hidaya'' . Izindi nyenyeri zigaragara zirimo Ayoub Bombwe na Godliver Gordian. <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8540608/</ref> <ref>https://torontoblackfilm.com/movie/bahasha/</ref>

Yagaragaye kandi muri ''Binti'' ya Seko Shamte, filime ikinamico yo muri Tanzaniya iteganijwe gusohoka mu 2021. Yakinnye nka "Roza". <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt11867140/?ref_=m_nm_knf_i3</ref>

